			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>From March 5-11, 2011, a team of four multimedia journalists collaborated with the MediaStorm team at our MediaStorm Multimedia Workshop. Participants spent a week reporting, editing, and producing <a href="http://mediastorm.com/training/the-amazing-amy">The Amazing Amy</a>.</p>
